MAPPING.DESCRIPTION: This Mapping fetches the data from LAWSON database POVAGRMTHD table and loads the data into MAKE_HOLD_HEADER table of TPROD1
MAPPING.NAME: m_MAKE_HOLD_HEADER

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: Fetches the required column values from source definition.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: SQ_POVAGRMTHD

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Sql Query
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT POVAGRMTHD.PROCURE_GROUP, POVAGRMTHD.VEN_AGRMT_REF, POVAGRMTHD.VENDOR, POVAGRMTHD.PURCH_FR_LOC, POVAGRMTHD.EFFECTIVE_DT, POVAGRMTHD.EXPIRE_DT, POVAGRMTHD.AGRMT_ADMIN, POVAGRMTHD.HOLD_FLAG, POVAGRMTHD.PO_NUMBER, POVAGRMTHD.R_STATUS FROM $$SCHEMA.POVAGRMTHD WHERE POVAGRMTHD.AGMT_TYPE = 'B' AND POVAGRMTHD.CLOSE_COMMIT_F <> 1 AND POVAGRMTHD.R_STATUS <> 3 AND POVAGRMTHD.EXPIRE_DT>SYSDATE AND (POVAGRMTHD.VEN_AGRMT_REF LIKE 'MH%' OR POVAGRMTHD.VEN_AGRMT_REF LIKE 'BH%')

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: We call the unconnected lookup to get R_NAME from POCONTACTS.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: EXP_MAKE_HOLD_HEADER

TRANSFORMATION.DESCRIPTION: We pass AGRMT_ADMIN of (POVAGRMTHD) and match it with AGRMT_ADMIN of(POCONTACTS) and fetch R_NAME from (POCONTACTS) in this lookup.
TRANSFORMATION.NAME: LKP_POCONTACTS

TABLEATTRIBUTE.NAME: Lookup Sql Override
TABLEATTRIBUTE.VALUE: SELECT POCONTACTS.R_NAME as R_NAME, POCONTACTS.AGRMT_ADMIN as AGRMT_ADMIN FROM $$SCHEMA.POCONTACTS

INSTANCE.DESCRIPTION: The Stored procedure truncates the target table(MAKE_HOLD_HEADER) of TPROD1

INSTANCE.DESCRIPTION: We pass AGRMT_ADMIN of (POVAGRMTHD) and match it with AGRMT_ADMIN of(POCONTACTS) and fetch R_NAME from (POCONTACTS) in this lookup.
INSTANCE.NAME: LKP_POCONTACTS
